      "message": "Note that this will be more expensive than the strncmp that it replaces. The strncmp would halt as soon as a mismatch is found - presumably in the first character or two in most cases. The conversion to StringPiece means that a full strlen has to be performed. I guess if the keys are short enough this doesn\u0027t matter but it still seems wasteful to do a strlen scan followed immediately by a strcmp scan.",
